Ning Jing!

34
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,390
Ning Jing, where are you?

35
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:41,759
Ning Jing,

36
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,710
where are you?

37
00:02:42,890 --> 00:02:44,200
Ning Jing!

38
00:02:44,730 --> 00:02:45,359
Ning Jing,

39
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,599
come back now!

40
