Ning Jing!

43
00:02:57,110 --> 00:02:58,900
(Ding Wei)

44
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:04,740
(Ding Wei)

45
00:03:06,544 --> 00:03:07,687
Yes, Ding Wei?

46
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:13,900
=Lies Never Lie=
=Episode 15=

47
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:14,599
Let me do it.

48
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,550
Okay.

49
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:37,729
Captain Ding,

50
00:03:37,730 --> 00:03:39,009
Ms. Luo didn't go to work today.

51
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:40,800
No one from the company
has been able to reach her.

52
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:43,480
Her phone is off, and she hasn't responded
to WeChat, QQ, or email.

53
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:47,200
- When was the last time they talked to her?
- Yesterday evening before getting off work.

54
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:03,009
Officer!

55
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:04,110
Sir! Sir!

56
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:07,280
We got the report and went
to check immediately.

57
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,580
There's no one at Mr. Ning's house.

58
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,120
Any records of him leaving
the neighborhood?

59
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,919
No. But I checked the surveillance footage.

60
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:14,830
Mr. Ning entered the estate
at 6:30 PM yesterday

61
00:04:14,850 --> 00:04:16,200
and never left.

62
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,199
Look

63
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:18,839
at this.

64
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,399
Around 8 PM,

65
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:22,750
the elevator camera caught
him going downstairs.

66
00:04:22,810 --> 00:04:23,609
Right here.

67
00:04:23,610 --> 00:04:24,319
See?

68
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:27,160
This is the last footage of him.

69
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:30,400
But here's what's strange.
After stepping out of the elevator,

70
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:32,079
he never appeared

71
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,360
on any of the neighborhood's cameras.

72
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:35,399
Take a look.

73
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,129
I reviewed all of the footage.

74
00:04:37,130 --> 00:04:38,369
He just vanished.

75
00:04:38,370 --> 00:04:40,079
He was making a phone call around 8 PM.

76
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,049
Then he disappeared.

77
00:04:41,050 --> 00:04:41,959
Yes.

78
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:45,279
Check Ning Zhiyuan's call records.
Find out who he talked to at 8 PM.

79
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,110
Yes, sir.

80
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,609
Am I right?

81
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:49,450
Is Ning Zhiyuan's car still
in the neighborhood?

82
00:04:49,450 --> 00:04:50,639
Come on, take me there.

83
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,670
Okay.

84
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,240
Miss Luo.

85
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,990
Miss Luo, are you home?

86
00:04:59,050 --> 00:05:00,750
Miss Luo, are you home?

87
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,310
Open the door.

88
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,510
Hello, please come in.

89
00:05:09,610 --> 00:05:10,920
Miss Luo.

90
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:12,929
Miss Luo.

91
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:13,719
Check upstairs.

92
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:13,959
Okay.

93
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,040
Miss Luo.

94
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,839
I know that license plate number,

95
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,159
White W6021.

96
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,489
I already looked into it.

97
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:26,569
I had a feeling something
was off about Mr. Ning.

98
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:28,990
Years of reading detective novels
have taught me...

99
00:05:29,130 --> 00:05:30,280
Keep quiet.

100
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,809
(Li Mochou)
This is the car.

101
00:05:49,810 --> 00:05:51,430
It's Ning Zhiyuan's car.

102
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,510
Hello, Mochou.

103
00:06:00,570 --> 00:06:01,720
Hey, Zhiyuan.

104
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,240
It's me, Yue.

105
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,639
I found Ning Zhiyuan's car
in the basement parking lot.

106
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,870
The door was unlocked.

107
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,310
But he's not here.

108
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:10,720
His phone was in the car.

109
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,960
I'm checking his call records now.

110
00:06:14,490 --> 00:06:17,959
His last call was from Luo Yifei

111
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:20,040
at 8:02 PM.

112
00:06:21,490 --> 00:06:22,630
Wait a second.

113
00:06:41,610 --> 00:06:42,750
No one is at home,

114
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,430
and there are no signs of a struggle.

115
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:56,720
The meal box is still sealed,

116
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,280
and the chopsticks
haven't even been unwrapped.

117
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,639
At Luo Yifei's place,
we found an untouched takeout order.

118
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,159
Based on the receipt,

119
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,249
something must have happened

120
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,319
between 7 and 8 PM.

121
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,489
Otherwise,

122
00:07:08,490 --> 00:07:10,489
she wouldn't have left without eating.

123
00:07:10,490 --> 00:07:12,070
She's been unreachable ever since.

124
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,990
They've been kidnapped.

125
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,800
The blood test results are in.

126
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,840
The blood found in the parking lot
is Ning Zhiyuan's.

127
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:25,609
Anran, take a team and check all of Luo Yifei
and Ning Zhiyuan's accounts.

128
00:07:25,610 --> 00:07:27,670
- See if any transactions have been made.
- Yes, madam.

129
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:30,820
Liu, track Luo Yifei's phone in real time.
The moment it's turned on, get a location.

130
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:31,280
Yes, madam.

131
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:32,449
All right.

132
00:07:32,450 --> 00:07:35,129
Let's check the surveillance footage

133
00:07:35,130 --> 00:07:37,250
from Ning Zhiyuan's
neighborhood parking lot last night.

134
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,959
At 8:03 PM,

135
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:42,199
he was last seen on camera,

136
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:44,310
heading down the fire escape
into the parking lot.

137
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:47,569
Judging by his direction,
he was walking toward his parking spot.

138
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:50,489
But his parking spot is a blind spot
for the cameras. And then he vanished.

139
00:07:50,490 --> 00:07:52,960
There's no trace of him
on any surveillance footage after that.

140
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:55,430
We searched the entire parking lot
but found nothing.

141
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:57,519
Ning Zhiyuan's phone was left
in his car,

142
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,199
and the door was unlocked,
yet he was gone.

143
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,840
That means something happened to him
when he was heading to his car.

144
00:08:01,890 --> 00:08:03,040
Exactly.

145
00:08:03,490 --> 00:08:05,399
We also checked
the footage of all vehicles

146
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:07,369
that left the garage after 8 PM.

147
00:08:07,370 --> 00:08:08,719
This is what we found.

148
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,079
At 2:17 AM,

149
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:12,489
a cleaner was pushing
a massive garbage bin

150
00:08:12,490 --> 00:08:15,070
toward the blind spot
near Ning Zhiyuan's parking space.

151
00:08:16,450 --> 00:08:17,249
One minute later,

152
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:19,009
he reappeared in another camera,

153
00:08:19,010 --> 00:08:20,480
heading toward a corner parking spot.

154
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,719
That doesn't make sense.

155
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,889
No matter how hardworking,

156
00:08:25,890 --> 00:08:28,510
a cleaner wouldn't collect trash
at 2 AM.

157
00:08:28,890 --> 00:08:31,480
He slowed down and the amount
of strength used also differed.

158
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:34,080
The way he was pushing showed
he was struggling.

159
00:08:36,090 --> 00:08:37,600
The bin got heavier.

160
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,329
That's right.

161
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:40,129
After passing Ning Zhiyuan's car,

162
00:08:40,130 --> 00:08:42,600
the bin was noticeably heavier.

163
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:45,559
Ning Zhiyuan was likely

164
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,519
inside it.

165
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,680
Then,

166
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:49,849
at 2:23 AM,

167
00:08:49,850 --> 00:08:51,249
just five minutes later,

168
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:53,559
a gray SUV left the parking lot.

169
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,249
I suspect

170
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:56,910
that's how they transported
Ning Zhiyuan out.

171
00:08:59,090 --> 00:09:01,889
But the person pushing the bin
was wearing a mask and a hat,

172
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:03,320
so we couldn't identify him.

173
00:09:03,330 --> 00:09:04,480
Pause the video.

174
00:09:06,970 --> 00:09:07,960
Ding Wei,

175
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:10,320
what's that?

176
00:09:12,250 --> 00:09:13,440
Bandages.

177
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,910
Okay.

178
00:09:16,730 --> 00:09:18,249
Yue's team found the gray SUV abandoned

179
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:19,759
on a highway outside the city.

180
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,200
No one inside.

181
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:24,270
Meng Zhengyi and the two victims
are still missing.

182
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:37,519
Yue.

183
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,039
Yes?

184
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,679
- What's the situation?
- The driver said the SUV was already here

185
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,720
when they arrived.

186
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,440
But there are too many tire tracks
on the ground.

187
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,480
So we can't tell which one belongs
to Meng Zhengyi's car

188
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,919
or which direction they went.

189
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,480
But we suspect
they switched vehicles here.

190
00:09:59,070 --> 00:10:02,460
(Peace and Safety)

191
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,840
What's this?

192
00:10:11,210 --> 00:10:12,560
Peace and safety.

193
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,840
This is Ning Zhiyuan's amulet.

194
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:16,960
(Peace and Safety)
From the looks of the cord,

195
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,209
it was bitten off.

196
00:10:18,210 --> 00:10:20,089
That means
he was in a desperate situation.

197
00:10:20,090 --> 00:10:22,240
Meng Zhengyi may hurt them at any time.

198
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:24,519
- Yue! Anran!
- Yes, Captain Ding.

199
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,639
Pull all nearby surveillance footage

200
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:27,560
and look into everything.

201
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,480
Conduct a full-scale search for Meng Zhengyi
and prepare for a rescue operation.

202
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,480
- Yes, madam!
- Yes, madam!

203
00:10:46,950 --> 00:10:50,140
(Police Roadblock)

204
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,320
(Police)
Bank accounts belonging

205
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,840
to Ning Zhiyuan, Luo Yifei,
and Meng Zhengyi haven't been touched.

206
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:00,320
It's like they've vanished into thin air,
leaving no traces at all.

207
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,799
Meng Zhengyi is ruthless.

208
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:04,159
The victims have been in his hands
for 20 hours.

209
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,560
- Could they already be...
- No.

210
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:09,489
We have a citywide manhunt for him.

211
00:11:09,490 --> 00:11:10,519
Yet he's going

212
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:12,489
through all this effort to move them.

213
00:11:12,490 --> 00:11:14,840
That means these two hostages
are extremely important to him.

214
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,399
What does he want in exchange for them?

215
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,840
If he wants hostages,

216
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:21,159
that means Luo Yifei
and Ning Zhiyuan are still alive.

217
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:22,969
But we have no leads.

218
00:11:22,970 --> 00:11:24,089
We don't need to find him.

219
00:11:24,090 --> 00:11:25,720
He'll contact us himself.

220
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:29,609
Hello?

221
00:11:29,610 --> 00:11:30,360
Hello.

222
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,080
It's Meng Zhengyi.

223
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:44,329
This is Captain Ding Wei,
Baizhou Criminal Investigation Team 2.

224
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:46,639
I have the people you're looking for.

225
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,439
They are still alive.

226
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,630
What do you want?

227
00:11:50,090 --> 00:11:51,209
Half an hour from now.

228
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:52,489
Fuxing Harbor.

229
00:11:52,490 --> 00:11:54,369
Open a route for me to board a ship

230
00:11:54,370 --> 00:11:55,870
and leave the country.

231
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:59,039
I need to hear Mr. Ning
and Miss Luo's voices first.

232
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:01,729
Relax. They're alive.

233
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:04,110
Once I leave, I'll release them.

234
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:05,919
Hello?

235
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,080
Call back!

236
00:12:09,890 --> 00:12:11,030
The phone is off.

237
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,849
We were so close to track him down.

238
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:15,110
He's careful.

239
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:17,639
He knew we were tracking his call

240
00:12:17,640 --> 00:12:19,270
and hung up at the right moment.

241
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:22,439
We couldn't pinpoint his exact location.
But we got a general area.

242
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:24,110
He should be in the Qiaonan District.

243
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,089
Qiaonan District?

244
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:25,759
Yes.

245
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,329
Fuxing Harbor

246
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:27,630
is in the Qiaonan District.

247
00:12:29,090 --> 00:12:30,729
Get everything ready as he asked.

248
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:31,990
You're really letting him go?

249
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:32,849
Of course not.

250
00:12:32,850 --> 00:12:34,039
We have to catch him.

251
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,279
He's cunning.

252
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,759
If we don't make it look real

253
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,849
and show him a ship,

254
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:39,039
he won't show up.

255
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:41,009
So we pretend to cooperate

256
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,790
while preparing for his capture.

257
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,639
That's the plan.

258
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:48,159
Mochou, I need you and Tiaotiao
to dig into Meng Zhengyi's background

259
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,489
and create a psychological profile

260
00:12:49,490 --> 00:12:51,680
to analyze Meng Zhengyi's
possible next moves.

261
00:12:52,370 --> 00:12:54,249
Anran, contact customs.

262
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:55,960
Make the preparations
according to his demands.

263
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,680
We're in the open
while he's hiding in the dark.

264
00:12:57,680 --> 00:13:00,249
Get all the paperwork
and procedures in order.

265
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:00,889
Yes, madam.

266
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:01,329
Yue,

267
00:13:01,330 --> 00:13:04,889
borrow a few unfamiliar officers
from Team 1 and have them stake out the harbor

268
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:06,510
and prepare to take action when needed.

269
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,630
Yes, madam.

270
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:10,110
You should stay out of sight.
Meng Zhengyi has seen you before.

271
00:13:10,490 --> 00:13:11,630
Got it.

272
00:13:18,490 --> 00:13:20,150
Everyone, move out!

273
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:41,390
- What are you doing?
- Police investigation.

274
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,200
What's the matter, Captain Ding?

275
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,200
Liu,

276
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,990
