277
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:01,790
Almost ten years.

278
00:14:01,890 --> 00:14:03,560
Why?

279
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:06,600
You've handled
a few kidnapping cases, right?

280
00:14:07,090 --> 00:14:08,009
Yeah.

281
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:11,720
But they're mostly threats
and scare tactics.

282
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,480
How many hostages are usually taken?

283
00:14:14,010 --> 00:14:15,960
One, right?

284
00:14:16,130 --> 00:14:17,750
If it's a kidnapping,

285
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:19,960
one hostage is enough.

286
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,039
Two are harder to control
and increase the risk of exposure.

287
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:26,240
So why did Meng Zhengyi take
both of them?

288
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:32,559
Liu,

289
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:34,369
send me the recording of his call.

290
00:14:34,370 --> 00:14:35,150
Okay.

291
00:14:39,610 --> 00:14:42,329
When was the last time you saw Mr. Meng?

292
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:43,129
Did he do

293
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:45,680
anything unusual in the past few days?

294
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,270
I don't know.

295
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,560
Nothing out of the ordinary?

296
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:02,200
Any updates?

297
00:15:12,890 --> 00:15:14,039
Stay sharp.

298
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:15,209
That guy is tall

299
00:15:15,210 --> 00:15:16,009
and has long legs.

300
00:15:16,010 --> 00:15:17,360
I bet he runs fast too.

301
00:15:38,370 --> 00:15:40,609
I have the people you're looking for.

302
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:41,680
Both of them

303
00:15:42,730 --> 00:15:44,030
are still alive.

304
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,039
Half an hour from now.

305
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,159
Fuxing Harbor.

306
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,969
Open a route for me to board a ship

307
00:15:48,970 --> 00:15:50,480
and leave the country.

308
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:54,320
Relax. They're alive.

309
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:56,790
Once I leave, I'll release them.

310
00:15:58,490 --> 00:15:59,630
Stop.

311
00:16:00,210 --> 00:16:01,360
Play it again.

312
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:44,329
Target has shown up.

313
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:46,030
Be on high alert.

314
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:47,200
Copy that.

315
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:50,329
Open a route for me to board a ship

316
00:16:50,330 --> 00:16:51,840
and leave the country.

317
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,870
Relax. They're alive.

318
00:16:55,090 --> 00:16:56,679
Once I leave, I'll release them.

319
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,399
Hearing a foghorn in the background

320
00:16:58,400 --> 00:16:59,630
is normal at a harbor.

321
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,889
Isolate the part with the foghorn,

322
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:06,159
amplify the sound, and play it again.

323
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,270
Got it.

324
00:17:07,570 --> 00:17:09,960
Once I leave, I'll release them.

325
00:17:10,330 --> 00:17:12,199
Once I leave, I'll release them.

326
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,329
Stop.

327
00:17:13,330 --> 00:17:14,049
Turn up the volume

328
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:14,769
and play it again.

329
00:17:14,770 --> 00:17:15,590
Okay.

330
00:17:27,530 --> 00:17:29,240
Get ready! Move in!

331
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,089
Stop right there!

332
00:17:52,090 --> 00:17:53,270
Freeze!

333
00:17:54,090 --> 00:17:54,920
Don't move!

334
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,200
Hands up!

335
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,640
Get down!

336
00:18:00,130 --> 00:18:02,919
That sound doesn't seem like a harbor.
It sounds more like...

337
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:04,719
- A railway crossing alarm.
- Yes, that's it.

338
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,329
A foghorn isn't only at a harbor.

339
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:08,070
It could be a train crossing.

340
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,569
We got it wrong.

341
00:18:09,570 --> 00:18:11,340
(Baizhou Criminal Investigation Team)

342
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,199
Hello?

343
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:17,529
Yue, Meng Zhengyi isn't at the harbor.

344
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:18,479
It was a setup!

345
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:19,129
Get up!

346
00:18:19,130 --> 00:18:20,270
Get him up!

347
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,750
Get up!

348
00:18:26,770 --> 00:18:27,720
Yue,

349
00:18:27,890 --> 00:18:28,830
these are just bricks.

350
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:31,399
- Where's Meng Zhengyi?
- I don't know who that is.

351
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:32,750
Who sent you?

352
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,240
A guy paid me.

353
00:18:41,810 --> 00:18:42,990
It was a homeless man.

354
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:43,609
He said

355
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:44,609
about an hour ago,

356
00:18:44,610 --> 00:18:46,439
some man gave him 1,000 yuan,

357
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,609
dressed him up,

358
00:18:47,610 --> 00:18:49,529
and told him to drive the car here

359
00:18:49,530 --> 00:18:51,400
and hand over the suitcase
to the police.

360
00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:53,129
He doesn't know anything else.

361
00:18:53,130 --> 00:18:55,600
(Overpass. Blind Massage. Grey Bin)
I think that man was Meng Zhengyi.

362
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:57,239
Look into these places.

363
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,199
This was the last place
Meng Zhengyi was seen.

364
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,880
Under the overpass.

365
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,389
The homeless guy said
there was a blind massage parlor nearby,

366
00:19:03,389 --> 00:19:04,889
a small two-story inn,

367
00:19:04,890 --> 00:19:07,529
and a gray metal dumpster.

368
00:19:07,530 --> 00:19:08,480
That's all he remembers?

369
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,690
That's all we could get from him.
Look into these first.

370
00:19:10,890 --> 00:19:14,400
Find locations within an hour's drive

371
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:18,719
from the harbor that have a railway crossing
and match these places.

372
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,550
On it.

373
00:19:19,570 --> 00:19:22,200
Mochou, check out that area.

374
00:19:26,130 --> 00:19:26,809
Mochou,

375
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:27,960
look.

376
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:42,350
He's a stalker.

377
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,640
And worse, he's a fetishist.

378
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,399
Yes, Mochou?

379
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,200
Ding Wei,

380
00:20:01,370 --> 00:20:02,399
something is not right.

381
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,830
Okay. Meng Zhengyi set this up
as a distraction.

382
00:20:06,290 --> 00:20:09,360
I found Meng Zhengyi stashing
Luo Yifei's personal belongings.

383
00:20:09,360 --> 00:20:11,479
He's obsessed with her,
almost to the point of madness.

384
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:13,089
His possessiveness is extreme.

385
00:20:13,090 --> 00:20:14,479
He would never

386
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,129
let her be

387
00:20:16,130 --> 00:20:17,480
with another man.

388
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:21,270
And another thing, Meng Zhengyi has been
taking medication for bipolar disorder.

389
00:20:21,290 --> 00:20:22,889
So he's incredibly dangerous.

390
00:20:22,890 --> 00:20:25,239
He could do something extreme
at any moment.

391
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:28,129
That phone call was a decoy.

392
00:20:28,130 --> 00:20:29,679
It was just to buy time.

393
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:30,769
Meng Zhengyi didn't kidnap

394
00:20:30,770 --> 00:20:32,089
Luo Yifei and Ning Zhiyuan

395
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:34,400
to escape.

396
00:20:35,050 --> 00:20:37,639
If that were his goal,
he would have killed them on the spot

397
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,400
instead of setting up this whole scheme.

398
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:42,889
Meng Zhengyi is going through all this trouble,
playing cat and mouse with the police.

399
00:20:42,890 --> 00:20:44,790
There must be a reason.

400
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:49,680
That's right, his goal is to kill.

401
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:52,310
He set up a diversion

402
00:20:53,130 --> 00:20:54,550
to buy time.

403
00:20:55,890 --> 00:20:58,159
That means
he's still somewhere in Baizhou.

404
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:01,369
Right now, he's trying to reach
the place he chose for the murder

405
00:21:01,370 --> 00:21:04,369
while leading the police
toward the harbor.

406
00:21:04,370 --> 00:21:06,049
That means the place he wanted to go

407
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:08,400
must be in the opposite direction.

408
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,089
Liu.

409
00:21:10,090 --> 00:21:10,439
Yes?

410
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,959
Tell the team

411
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:14,569
to conduct a full sweep of this area.

412
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:15,720
Yes, madam.

413
00:21:27,370 --> 00:21:28,200
Captain Ding.

414
00:21:29,050 --> 00:21:30,919
Set up roadblocks on all major routes

415
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:31,959
near Beishan Bridge.

416
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:34,239
Search every possible hiding spot.

417
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,269
Yes, madam!

418
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:39,060
(Serve the People)

419
00:21:48,330 --> 00:21:50,070
Nothing on my end.

420
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,830
- You?
- None.

421
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:56,030
Still nothing.

422
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:58,510
No sign of him.

423
00:21:59,200 --> 00:21:59,990
Ning Jing.

424
00:22:01,770 --> 00:22:03,480
Zeng Xiang.

425
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:06,920
Bao Xijie. Xu Jun.

426
00:22:10,890 --> 00:22:12,529
There's no connection

427
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:14,199
between their crime scenes.

428
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:14,809
Yes,

429
00:22:14,810 --> 00:22:16,089
all the locations seem random

430
00:22:16,090 --> 00:22:17,769
with no special connections.

431
00:22:17,770 --> 00:22:19,310
No sign of Meng Zhengyi.

432
00:22:22,640 --> 00:22:24,200
- Nothing here.
- No sign of him.

433
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,750
I have nothing here.

434
00:22:29,810 --> 00:22:31,919
But Luo Yifei is extremely important

435
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,270
to him.

436
00:22:33,530 --> 00:22:36,369
He wouldn't just take them
somewhere random to kill them.

437
00:22:36,370 --> 00:22:37,959
He must have brought her

438
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,089
to a place

439
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:40,920
that holds special meaning to him.

440
00:22:41,290 --> 00:22:42,920
Somewhere special.

441
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:24,529
Check the cars over there.

442
00:23:24,530 --> 00:23:25,750
Yes.

443
00:23:28,050 --> 00:23:29,880
- Find anything?
- Nothing.

444
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:32,920
Captain Ding, I caught a pickpocket while
searching and I've sent him back to the station.

445
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:34,479
But no sign of Meng Zhengyi. Over.

446
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,990
Still nothing here.

447
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,159
Find anything?

448
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:38,030
Nothing.

449
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:39,159
We've searched everywhere

450
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,590
but we find nothing.

451
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,479
Hello, Ding Wei.

452
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,880
This isn't working.

453
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,880
We're looking
for a needle in a haystack.

454
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:32,480
The longer this takes,

455
00:24:32,530 --> 00:24:34,569
the more danger Ning Zhiyuan
and Luo Yifei are in.

456
00:24:34,570 --> 00:24:35,750
I know.

457
00:24:36,290 --> 00:24:37,369
Are you okay?

458
00:24:37,370 --> 00:24:38,510
I'm okay.

459
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:40,199
Stay focused.

460
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,529
Don't let the past.

461
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:43,070
and personal feelings get in the way.

462
00:24:43,530 --> 00:24:44,399
Use your expertise.

463
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:47,310
I believe in you. Just give me a direction.
I will definitely find them.

464
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:48,609
Okay.

465
00:24:48,610 --> 00:24:50,200
I can do this.

466
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:15,529
Ms. Wei, I've been searching
for ages but I didn't find anything.

467
00:25:15,530 --> 00:25:16,880
What about Ms. Li?

468
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,200
Have faith in her. She'll figure it out.

469
00:25:22,370 --> 00:25:23,439
Keep searching!

470
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,350
Yes!

471
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:39,159
Hello?

472
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,159
I found it.

473
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:43,289
Three years ago,
Meng Zhengyi adopted a tiger

474
00:25:43,290 --> 00:25:44,550
and named it Zhengyi

475
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,560
(Animal Adoption Agreement)
after one of his name characters

476
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:47,830
and the number "one."

477
00:25:48,290 --> 00:25:51,440
The tiger is now
at Beishan Bridge Wildlife Park.

478
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:53,609
That's it.

479
00:25:53,610 --> 00:25:54,680
That has to be the place.

480
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:57,160
Call Captain Ding immediately
and dispatch a team over there now.

481
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,239
Yes.

482
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,960
Ms. Wei, they've figured it out.

483
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:04,030
Meng Zhengyi is at No. 88, Beishan Bay.

484
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:08,030
Everyone, move out
to No. 88, Beishan Bay.

485
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,679
Let's go!

486
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:10,830
Yes, madam.

487
00:26:29,230 --> 00:26:33,620
