00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:38,809
Yifei.

489
00:26:38,810 --> 00:26:39,920
Yifei.

490
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,830
Yifei.

491
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:44,830
Are you okay?

492
00:26:53,770 --> 00:26:56,049
Mr. Meng, this is illegal.

493
00:26:56,050 --> 00:26:57,480
Let us go, please.

494
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,750
Are you scared?

495
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,640
Don't be scared.

496
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:23,070
You know I love you.

497
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,160
Look at me!

498
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:31,270
Always bossing me around, huh?

499
00:27:32,850 --> 00:27:34,030
Hush...

500
00:27:36,290 --> 00:27:39,030
It won't hurt. I'll tear it off gently.

501
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:42,070
Zhengyi,

502
00:27:42,330 --> 00:27:43,399
let us go,

503
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,199
okay?

504
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,439
I promise

505
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,679
we won't call the police.

506
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,070
"We?"

507
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,880
Yifei,

508
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:53,479
I did everything for you.

509
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:55,200
I have nothing left.

510
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,529
And you betrayed me

511
00:27:56,530 --> 00:27:57,750
for this pretty boy.

512
00:27:58,370 --> 00:27:59,750
You chose him over me?

513
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,830
Huh?

514
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:03,679
No, don't!

515
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,999
Zhengyi. Zhengyi.

516
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:05,959
I'll kill you!

517
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:06,830
Zhengyi! Zhengyi!

518
00:28:06,850 --> 00:28:08,369
What's so great about him?

519
00:28:08,370 --> 00:28:09,310
Zhengyi,

520
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,809
I'm begging you.

521
00:28:10,810 --> 00:28:12,529
Zhengyi, please.

522
00:28:12,530 --> 00:28:13,790
Let me go,

523
00:28:14,130 --> 00:28:15,350
and I swear we...

524
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,959
I mean I won't call the police.
