525
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:18,889
I won't call the police.

526
00:28:18,890 --> 00:28:21,880
- Just let him go.
- Let him go? That's impossible.

527
00:28:22,290 --> 00:28:23,640
He must die.

528
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,480
He must die today.

529
00:28:26,130 --> 00:28:27,809
Zhengyi. Meng Zhengyi!

530
00:28:27,810 --> 00:28:29,750
Meng Zhengyi, are you crazy?

531
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:32,640
What are you trying to do?

532
00:28:32,770 --> 00:28:33,550
What are you doing?

533
00:28:38,530 --> 00:28:40,350
Meng Zhengyi, are you crazy?

534
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:41,849
Yeah.

535
00:28:41,850 --> 00:28:43,529
I'm crazy.

536
00:28:43,530 --> 00:28:44,680
Come here.

537
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:46,070
No!

538
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,200
Don't do it!

539
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,750
Zhengyi.

540
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:55,270
Don't do it, please.

541
00:28:55,610 --> 00:28:56,920
I'm begging you. Please don't.

542
00:28:57,090 --> 00:28:58,120
Beg me?

543
00:28:58,290 --> 00:28:59,480
What are you begging for?

544
00:28:59,530 --> 00:29:02,400
I'm begging you not to kill him, okay?

545
00:29:02,570 --> 00:29:04,399
I lost everything because of you.

546
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,199
Now I'm a wanted man.

547
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,289
I'm as good as dead!

548
00:29:07,290 --> 00:29:08,889
